tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE leadership_metrics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  leader_name VARCHAR,
  team_size INT,
  communication_score FLOAT,
  decision_making_score FLOAT,
  productivity_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    leader_name VARCHAR(255),
    performance_score FLOAT,
    leadership_style VARCHAR(100),
    team_size INT
);

CREATE TABLE feedback_metrics (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    performance_rating INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    reviewer_name VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE leadership_skills (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    leader_name VARCHAR(255),
    communication_skills INT,
    decision_making_skills INT,
    strategic_thinking INT
);

CREATE TABLE team_metrics (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    team_name VARCHAR(255),
    team_size INT,
    team_performance_score FLOAT,
    team_communication_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE LeadershipMetrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    leader_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value FLOAT,
    metric_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE LeadershipScores (
    score_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    leader_id INT,
    score_type VARCHAR(50),
    score_value FLOAT,
    score_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE LeadershipRatings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    leader_id INT,
    rating_category VARCHAR(50),
    rating_score INT,
    rating_date DATE
);
